window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>A war unlike any other has started.</b></p> <p>Genevieve Beaufont is the only one who can end it.</p> <p><b>What happens next will decide the fate of the world.</b></p> <p>Magicians and mortals have battled for ages. Either one will survive or both could die. The opportunity for peace between the races depends on one child.</p> <p><b>If he survives, then magic stands a chance.</b> If Gen Beaufont can't save him, then her people will perish.</p> <p><b>Will magicians finally become extinct, unable to coexist with the world of mortals?</b></p> <p>Or can the Beaufonts do what they were always meant to and save magicâ€”protecting the world that Mother Nature entrusted them to? The next battles will decide how a thousand year story ends.</p>"; 
